---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="页面不存在">
  <section class="page-header shell-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">404</p>
    <h1>页面不存在</h1>
    <p>这个地址可能已经变更，或者暂时还没有对应内容。你可以回首页、按标签继续找，或者直接搜索。</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="hero-action is-primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
      <a class="hero-action" href="/tags/">查看标签</a>
      <a class="hero-action" href="/search/">站内搜索</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
